title: BOB HOPE COMEDY SPECIAL -- with Lucille Ball, Joan Collins, etc.
description:
This opened the 1966 to 67 TV season with an all-star guest cast, mainly 
consisting of 15 of Bob Hope's many leading ladies in movies over the years, 
most of whom were only in their 40s by that time.

With Lucille Ball, Joan Caulfield, Joan Collins, Arlene Dahl, Phyllis Diller, 
Rhonda Fleming, Joan Fontaine, Signe Hasso, Hedy Lamarr, Dorothy Lamour, 
Marilyn Maxwell, Virginia Mayo, Dina Merrill, Vera Miles, Janis Paige, 
Jerry Colonna, Paul Lynde, and Ken Murray
